* The predator saw the raptors break from the flesh ripping grip and saw 
that they now stood apart, now it had to decide which one to attack.
The carnivour felt it's stomach rummble and complain, it was ready to be 
fed!
The predator crept a few more feet towards the striped reptiles, it stopped 
and sniffed the air, one of then seemed aware that it was hunting!
It was then that the predator flexed it's muscles and moved into action, it 
had crept so close that in one stride it soon menaced over the back of one 
of the reptiles and brought it's massive jaws down on it's spine.
It sank it's teeth deep into the back of the biggest of the two raptors, the 
8 inch fangs digging in fiercely!
It had surprised it's prey!*
